msgctxt "sn20.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 20 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 20 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Opammavagga "
msgstr "1. Similes "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 2. Nakhasikhasutta → nakhasikkhāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn20.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Nakhasikhasutta "
msgstr "2. A Fingernail "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn20.2:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.2:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā parittaṃ nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsuṃ āropetvā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha, picking up a little bit of dirt under his fingernail, addressed the mendicants: "

msgctxt "sn20.2:1.3"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "“What do you think, mendicants? "

#. VAR: cāyaṃ → ayaṃ vā (bj) | yā cāyam (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn20.2:1.4"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yo cāyaṃ mayā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito yā cāyaṃ mahāpathavī”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the little bit of dirt under my fingernail, or this great earth?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.2:1.5"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ yadidaṃ mahāpathavī. "
msgstr "“Sir, the great earth is far more. "

msgctxt "sn20.2:1.6"
msgid "Appamattakoyaṃ bhagavatā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito. "
msgstr "The little bit of dirt under your fingernail is tiny. "

msgctxt "sn20.2:1.7"
msgid "Saṅkhampi na upeti upanidhimpi na upeti kalabhāgampi na upeti mahāpathaviṃ upanidhāya bhagavatā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the great earth, it can’t be reckoned or compared, it’s not even a fraction.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.2:1.8"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, appakā te sattā ye manussesu paccājāyanti; "
msgstr "“In the same way the sentient beings reborn as humans are few, "

msgctxt "sn20.2:1.9"
msgid "atha kho eteyeva bahutarā sattā ye aññatra manussehi paccājāyanti. "
msgstr "while those not reborn as humans are many. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.2:1.10"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "sn20.2:1.11"
msgid "‘appamattā viharissāmā’ti. "
msgstr "‘We will stay diligent.’ "

msgctxt "sn20.2:1.12"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn20.2:1.13"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

